<codeline lineno="33"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@code{.cpp}</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="34"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>//<sp/>Create<sp/>two<sp/>nodes</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="35"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>Node<sp/>node1(1);</highlight></codeline>
